&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The Rajdhani Train&amp;nbsp;came&amp;nbsp;into operation on&lt;b&gt; 1 March 1969.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;First Rajdhani Train&lt;/strong&gt; embarked on its maiden journey on&amp;nbsp; &lt;strong&gt;3&lt;sup&gt;rd&lt;/sup&gt; March 1969&lt;/strong&gt; from &lt;strong&gt;Howrah&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;As per the dynamic pricing system of Indian Railways, only the first &lt;strong&gt;10%&lt;/strong&gt; tickets sold in Rajdhani, Shatabdi, and Duronto trains are available at the fares listed from the root room.&lt;/li&gt;
